# Settings & Config

1. remove vertical gray line
 - Wrap-Guide Enable > Disable

2. auto trailing white space disable
 - File > Settings > Editor > Editor Settings > Packages list
 - search 'whitespace'
 - Whitespace > Settings > Remove Trailing whitespace (uncheck)
  or 
 - File > Config
   whitespace:
    removeTrailingWhitespace: false

3. install minimap
 - File > Settings > install
 - search 'minimap' > install

